name: Numeric
description: Numeric value, including integer or float (e.g., creatinine, weight)

name: Coded
description: Value determined by term dictionary lookup (i.e., term identifier)

name: None
description: Not associated with a datatype (e.g., term answers, sets)

name: Document
description: Pointer to a binary or text-based document (e.g., clinical document, RTF, XML, EKG, image, etc.) stored in complex_obs table

name: Complex
description: Complex value. Analogous to HL7 Embedded Datatype
